text: The canton of La Vallée de la Têt is an administrative division of the Pyrénées-Orientales department, in southern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Le Soler.Décret n° 2014-262 du 26 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département des Pyrénées-Orientales It consists of the following communes: #Corbère #Corbère-les-Cabanes #Corneilla-la-Rivière #Ille- sur-Têt #Millas #Montalba-le-Château #Néfiach #Saint-Féliu-d'Amont #Saint- Féliu-d'Avall #Le Soler ==References== Category:Cantons of Pyrénées-Orientales
